window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Gavin Guile is dying.</p> <p>He’d thought he had five years left - now he has less than one. With 50,000 refugees, a bastard son, and an ex-fiancée who may have learned his darkest secret, Gavin has problems on every side. All magic in the world is running wild and threatens to destroy the Seven Satrapies.</p> <p>Worst of all, the old gods are being reborn, and their army of color wights is unstoppable. The only salvation may be the brother whose freedom and life Gavin stole 16 years ago.</p> <p>Performed by Richard Rohan, Christopher Scheeren, Joe Brack, Karen Novak, Steven Carpenter, Kimberly Gilbert, Elliot Dash, Tracy Olivera, Michael John Casey, Laura Reichert, David Coyne, David Harris, Tim Getman, James Konicek, Eric Messner, Sunny Lasskey, Margie Tompros, Thomas Keegan, Daniel Sontagg, Thomas Penny, Michael Glenn, Casie Platt, Colleen Delany, Dylan Lynch, Drew Kopas, Anastasia Wilson, Patrick Bussink, Tim Carlin, Nick DePinto, Alyssa Wilmoth, Joel David Santner, Johann Dettweiler, Christopher Graybill, Bradley Smith, Robert Collins, Nanette Savard, James Lewis, Delores King Williams, Gary Telles, Yasmin Tuazon, Evan Casey, Ken Jackson, Jessica Lefkow, Katy Carkuff, Elizabeth Jernigan, Barbara Pinolini, Ren Casey, Lily Beacon.</p>"; 
